{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dac80de4d5","title":"在胡乔木关于抗战胜利纪念日的请示报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"807ac40051","index":0,"year":1951,"month":8,"day":1,"articleId":"dac80de4d5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"bc39207ed5","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡乔木，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长、中央人民政府新闻总署署长。"},{"id":"1f2c0659e5","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"遵照毛泽东的指示，胡乔木于1951年8月2日为中央起草了一个给东北局并各中央局、各分局、各军区，并转各省市区党委及志愿军政治部的电报。电报说：“同意规定九月三日为全国统一的战胜日本纪念日，除东北应改在此日庆祝解放外，全国军民及报纸均应于此日纪念八年抗日战争的胜利。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"417a5e9dc6","type":"title","text":"在胡乔术叫关于抗战胜利纪念日的请示报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5"},{"id":"bc39207ed5","type":"paragraph","text":"请乔木另拟一电，采用统一的“九三”纪念","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5"},{"id":"1f2c0659e5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5"},{"id":"a3fe32e701","type":"paragraph","text":"八月一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5"}],"page":{"id":"c9a544e9a7","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"dac80de4d5","start":465,"end":465}}}},"__N_SSG":true}